Import/Export

Import

In Cone Mapper app it is possible to import cone locations from CSV files.
There are 2 possibilities to import data.
  1. Import as "New Recognition". In that option data will be placed on image as it is.
  2. Import as "Import Cone Locations". In that option user can move set of imported cones and decide where to place them.

Export

In Cone Mapper app it is possible to export cone locations to CSV files.
There are a few options:
  • Export whole image data
  • Export only selected rectangle
For each you also can decide:
  • Export selection as one file
  • Export selection as set of tiles of given size
The result of export is the two files (or set of pairs of files):
  • .tiff image
  • .csv table with cone locations
